import { Tabs,Tab, Toolbar, Typography,  } from '@mui/material';
import AppBar from '@mui/material/AppBar';
 
export const Navbar=()=>{

 

    return( 
        <>
        <AppBar elevation={0} sx={{ p: 3,pt:5 }}  >
            <Toolbar disableGutters>
               <Tabs>
                   <Tab>
                   <Typography>
                       Logo
                   </Typography>
                   </Tab>
                   <Tab label='HOME'/>
                   <Tab label='ABOUT'/>
                   <Tab label='SERVICES'/>
                   <Tab label='CONTACT'/>
               </Tabs>
            </Toolbar>
          
        </AppBar>
        </>
    )
}
